title: Bajaj Finance Q4 Preview: Expect another strong quarter with PAT growth of up to 80% - Economic Times
content: Bajaj Finance Q4 Preview: Expect another strong quarter with PAT growth of up to 80%  Economic Times
description: The Bajaj Group crown jewel is likely to report 33 per cent growth in NII, said analysts. They had a varied projection on profit growth for the quarter, in the range of 47-80 per cent YoY.
